xaxipcie_hw.h File Reference

Detailed Description

This header file contains identifiers and basic driver functions for the XAxiPcie device driver.

Note:
None.
 MODIFICATION HISTORY:

 Ver   Who  Date     Changes
 ----- ---- -------- -----------------------------------------------
 1.00a rkv  03/03/11  Original code.
 2.00a nm   09/19/11  Root port related changes are done.

#include "xil_types.h"
#include "xil_io.h"

RegOffset   )     Xil_In32((BaseAddress) + (RegOffset))
 

Macro to read register.

Parameters:
BaseAddress is the base address of the PCIe.
RegOffset is the register offset.
Returns:
Value of the register.
Note:
C-style signature: u32 XAxiPcie_ReadReg(u32 BaseAddress, u32 RegOffset)
